cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.DS, cs.SY 

This paper deals with decision making under uncertainty and risk, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also presents an algorithm for solving the problem, which falls under the category of optimization (cs.RO). The use of Markov decision processes (MDPs) and numerical experiments suggest that the paper may also be relevant to the fields of data science (cs.DS) and control systems (cs.SY).
